text: Coux is a commune of the Ardèche département in the south-east of France. The commune has a population of 1,466 people as of the year 1999.http://www.insee.fr/fr/recensement/nouv_recens/resultats/repartition/comd07.htm?numdep=07&x;=39&y;=7 List of population and communes of the Ardeche department ==Related pages== *Communes of the Ardèche department ==References== Category:Communes in Ardèche
title: Coux, Ardèche
